===Glyph origin===
{{Han etym}}
{{Han compound|示|見|c1=p|c2=s|t2=see|ls=psc}}.

Related to {{zh-l|*見|to see; to meet}}. The Chu form did not include the phonetic {{zh-l|*示}} component, making it near-identical to {{zh-l|*見}}, but with the lower component a kneeling figure rather than a standing one. ({{zh-ref|Galambos, 2006}})

