===Definitions===
{{head|zh|hanzi}} {{tlb|zh|literary|or in compounds}}

# to [[watch]]; to [[look]]; to [[view]]; to [[look at]]; {{n-g|compare {{m|zh|見|t=to see}}.}}
#* {{zh-x|非 禮 勿 視，非 禮 勿 聽，非 禮 勿 言，非 禮 勿 動。|ref=Lunyu|If it is not propriety, do not '''look at''' it. If it is not propriety, do not listen to it. If it is not propriety, do not speak it out. If it is not propriety, do not act it out.}}
#* {{zh-x|ref=Liji|鬼神 之 為 德，其 盛 矣 乎！視 之 而 弗 見，聽 之 而 弗 聞，體 物 而 不 可 遺。|The spirits' manifestation of potency: how abundant it is! We '''watch for''' them and do not see them; we listen for them and do not hear them. [Yet] they are the essences of things, and cannot be discarded.}}
## to [[inspect]]; to [[examine]]
##* {{zh-x|ref=Guoyu|^叔-魚 生，其 母 視 之，曰：「是 虎 目 而 豕 喙，鳶 肩 而 牛 腹，谿壑 可 盈，是 不 可 饜 也，必 以 賄 死。」遂 不 @視。|When Shuyu was born, his mother '''examined''' him. She said, "These are a tiger's eyes and a swine's mouth, a kite-bird's shoulders and a cow's belly. Even if a gorge can be filled, his greed cannot be sated. He will surely die from taking bribes." Then she did not take care of him.}}
## to [[regard]] as; to [[consider]] as; to [[take]] as
##* {{zh-x|ref=Lunyu|回 也 視 予 猶 父 也，予 不 得 視 猶 子 也。|Hui '''saw''' me as a father; I could not see him as a son.}}
## to [[visit]]
##* {{zh-x|ref=Lunyu|疾，君 視 之，東首，加 朝服，拖 紳。|He was ill, and the ruler '''visited''' him. He faced east, wore his court robes, and put on his girdle.}}
## to [[follow]] the example of; to [[take]] as one's [[model]]; to [[pattern]] after; to [[imitate]]
##* {{zh-x|ref=Shujing|王 懋 乃 德，視 乃 厥 祖，無 時 豫怠。|O king, strive for your potency; '''follow the example of''' your grandfather; do not be indulgent for a single moment.}}
## to [[deal with]]; to [[manage]]; to [[care for]]
##* {{zh-x|ref=Guoyu|^叔-魚 生，其 母 @視 之，曰：「是 虎 目 而 豕 喙，鳶 肩 而 牛 腹，谿壑 可 盈，是 不 可 饜 也，必 以 賄 死。」遂 不 視。|When Shuyu was born, his mother examined him. She said, "These are a tiger's eyes and a swine's mouth, a kite-bird's shoulders and a cow's belly. Even if a gorge can be filled, his greed cannot be sated. He will surely die from taking bribes." Then she did not '''take care of''' him.}}
# to [[compare]] with
## to be [[comparable]]
##* {{zh-x|ref=Mencius|天子 之 卿 受 地 視 侯，大夫 受 地 視 伯，元士 受 地 視 子、男。|The Son of Heaven's ministers received land that '''compares with''' [the holdings of] a marquis. The high officers received land that '''compares with''' [the holdings of] a count. The senior knights received land that '''compares with''' [the holdings of] a viscount or marquis.}}
# [[eyesight]]; [[sight]]
#* {{zh-x|ref=Mozi|曰：「天子 之 視聽 也 神。」先王 之 言 曰：「非 神 也，夫{fú} 唯 能 使 人 之 耳目 助 己 視聽。」|They said, "The Son of Heaven's '''sight''' and hearing are divine!" The ancient kings said, "Not divine; it is only that they could make the people's ears and eyes aid their own '''sight''' and hearing."}}
